  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0baa\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gotabaya Rajapaksa should be arrested - International organization petitions Singapore Attorney General's Department",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The International Truth and Justice Project has filed a petition with the Singapore Attorney General's Department seeking the arrest of former Sri Lankan President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "According to Truth and Justice International, an international organization documenting human rights abuses, Gotabaya Rajapaksa committed massive human rights violations while serving as Sri Lanka's defense secretary in 2009.",
        "The South Africa-based organization has said that investigations can be conducted in Singapore based on international jurisprudence regarding alleged human rights violations."
      ],
